        <div class="InsideBlock" id="Why_Choose_MLSI">
            <div class="InsideBlockHeader">
                Why choose MLSI
            </div>
            <div class="InsideBlockBody">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <p>
                            Choosing the right school for your child can be an overwhelming task for the parents due to numerous options available.However, transparency is the key aspect which parents should thrive for.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Right from the admission process, MLSI strives to be transparent and open with our parents as they are an integral part of our learning community.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We are open about our educational philosophy and welcome parents to join our team who believe in our approach.
                        </p>
                        <p class="strong black">
                            Here are some fundamentals of our approach to education which runs through PYP, DP, and MYP curriculum:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="checklist">
                            <li>Each child is treated as an individual who is unique.                             </li>
                            <li>Students are involved in real-world problem solving and learning.                 </li>
                            <li>Students engage in learning activities that are collaborative.                    </li>
                            <li>Students get ample opportunities to showcase their learning.                      </li>
                            <li>Students are encouraged to love and respect one another.                          </li>
                            <li>Students are explained the importance of setting high expectations for themselves.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
